<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to GridScout</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            color-scheme: dark;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1f2937 0%, #111827 50%, #0b1020 100%);
            color: #e5e7eb;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 820px;
            background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.92);
            border: 1px solid #374151;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 34px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #f9fafb;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        p {
            color: #d1d5db;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 14px 0;
        }

        ul {
            margin: 16px 0 24px 18px;
            color: #d1d5db;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .button-primary {
            background: #5865f2;
            border-color: #5865f2;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .button-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border-color: #4b5563;
            color: #e5e7eb;
        }

        .small {
            margin-top: 18px;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="card">
        <h1>Welcome to GridScout</h1>
        <p>
            GridScout is the central log and visibility service for scout activity and sightings across your Discord
            communities.
            Scouts submit reports over HTTP from the GridScout client, and this service aggregates those into a shared,
            searchable log.
        </p>
        <p>
            Built for <strong>EVE Online</strong> operations, GridScout helps fleets and intel teams maintain awareness
            of active scouts, local threats, and coverage status.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Collects scout pings, sightings, and activation signals in real time.</li>
            <li>Associates reports with Discord identities for secure, role-based access.</li>
            <li>Lets server admins control who can view operational logs via Discord roles.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            To continue, sign in with Discord so GridScout can verify your server membership and permissions.
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="<%= fix_path('/auth/discord/login') %>">Login using Discord</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="<%= fix_path('/install') %>">Install Client</a>
        </div>

        <p class="small">Already signed in users with a configured viewer role will be taken directly to the live logs.</p>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
